


cook 
 - 300 g buckwheat pasts
rinse
set aside

combine
 - 1/2 cup vegetable broth
 - 3 tbsp soy sauce
 - 1 tbsp mirin
 - 1 tbsp hoisin sauce
 - 1 tbsp fresh grated ginger
 - 1 grated garlic clove
set aside

prepare
 - 1 cup grated carrots
 - 1/2 cup grated radished
 - 2 minced green onions split between green and white parts
 - 1 cup minced boston lettuce
 - 1/2 cup cilantro
 - 1/3 cup chopped peanuts

combine
 - 1 lbs diced tofu
 - 1/4 cup corn startch
 - 1/2 tsp chinese 5 sipce

cook tofu in a large pan
set aside
add sauce
add white part of green onions
simmer covered 2 minutes
let cool
add pasta to a bowl
top with vegetables and tofu
stir into sauce
 - 1 tsp corn startch
bring to simmer until thickened
pour onto tofu
top with cilantro and peanuts

serves 3-4

#quick
